3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image retrieval, which is a type of multimedia retrieval. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses multiple assignment to improve recall, which is a machine learning technique. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper involves natural language processing in terms of describing the problem and the proposed solution.
